## Template Usage

This project was created from a [Copier](https://copier.readthedocs.io/) template.

To use this template for a new project:

```bash
copier copy path/to/templates/python-pkg my-new-project
```

## Development

This project uses `uv` for dependency management and `just` for task automation.

### Setup

```bash
just setup
```

### Running Tests

```bash
just test
```

### QA (Lint, Typecheck, Test)

```bash
just qa
```

